        "baseRefName": "master",
        "body": "This PR adds a version of the Cauchy-Schwarz inequality for positive semidefinite bilinear forms on modules over linearly ordered commutative rings, and applies it to restrict Coxeter weights for root systems.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n[![Open in Gitpod](https://gitpod.io/button/open-in-gitpod.svg)](https://gitpod.io/from-referrer/)\r\n",
        "changedFiles": 5,
        "closed": false,
        "closedAt": null,
        "comments": {
          "nodes": [
            {
              "id": "IC_kwDOFcwZ1c6UiVcf",
              "body": "### PR summary [c684d2d61e](https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/19343/commits/c684d2d61e5b92510ba9eb26827e3e8932ddd03d)\n\n<details><summary>\n\n#### Import changes for modified files\n\n</summary>\n\nDependency changes\n\n| File | Base Count | Head Count | Change |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.RootSystem.Finite.CanonicalBilinear | 1375 | 1377 | +2 (+0.15%) |\n| Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.RootSystem.Finite.Nondegenerate | 1418 | 1419 | +1 (+0.07%) |\n\n\n<details><summary>Import changes for all files</summary>\n\n|Files|Import difference|\n|-|-|\n| `Mathlib.Algebra.Lie.Weights.RootSystem` `Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.RootSystem.Finite.Nondegenerate`|1|\n| `Mathlib.LinearAlgebra.RootSystem.Finite.CanonicalBilinear`|2|\n\n</details>\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n<details><summary>\n\n#### Declarations diff\n\n</summary>\n\n`+ coxeterWeight_eq_one_or_two_or_three`\n`+ coxeterWeight_le_four`\n`+ exists_int_eq_coxeterWeight`\n`+ four_smul_rootForm_sq_eq_coxeterWeight_smul`\n`+ infinite_of_linearIndependent_coxeterWeight_four`\n`+ inner_inner_smul_sub_eq`\n`+ inner_mul_inner_le`\n`+ inner_mul_inner_le_of_pos`\n`+ inner_mul_lt_inner_self`\n`+ not_LinearIndependent_of_inner_mul_eq`\n`+ toPerfectPairing_apply_CoPolarization`\n`+ toPerfectPairing_apply_apply_Polarization`\n`+ zero_le_inner_self_mul`\n<details>\n  <summary>You can run this locally as follows</summary>\n\n\n```bash\n## summary with just the declaration names:\n./scripts/declarations_diff.sh <optional_commit>\n\n## more verbose report:\n./scripts/declarations_diff.sh long <optional_commit>\n```\n</details>\n\nThe doc-module for `script/declarations_diff.sh` contains some details about this script.\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n<details><summary>No changes to technical debt.</summary>\n\nYou can run this locally as\n```\n./scripts/technical-debt-metrics.sh pr_summary\n```\n* The `relative` value is the weighted *sum* of the differences with weight given by the *inverse* of the current value of the statistic.\n* The `absolute` value is the `relative` value divided by the total sum of the inverses of the current values (i.e. the weighted *average* of the differences).\n</details>",
              "createdAt": "2024-11-21T18:57:45Z",
              "author": {
                "login": "github-actions"
              }
            },
